init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The film you are watching is your life, and you are watching it from the moment you are born until the moment you die.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see a lot of people in the line who look like you, and you are all talking about your lives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You also notice that you are the only one who doesn't remember their previous lives.
